headline: Can the New PAYR ETF Redefine Federated Hermes' (FHI) Approach to Income Strategies?
summary: Earlier this month, Federated Hermes introduced the Enhanced Income ETF (CBOE: PAYR), designed to generate consistent monthly cash flow by combining high-dividend equities with an options overlay strategy. This launch highlights Federated Hermes' continued expansion into income-focused ETF solutions aimed at meeting the needs of retirees and investors seeking disciplined risk management.
